These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, drama, zombie
1. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, begonia, dahlia
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Flower   | aconite | begonia | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, yellow, red
1. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Color   | turquise | yellow | red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, september, june
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Birthday   | november | june | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, taxi, helicopter
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Transport   | taxi | roller | helicopter |

